    public abstract class AbstractConfigTest
extends AbstractLockedPlatformMBeanServerTest
    Each test that relies on ConfigRegistryImpl needs to subclass this test. ConfigRegistryImpl is registered to platform MBean Server using initConfigTransactionManagerImpl(org.opendaylight.controller.config.manager.impl.factoriesresolver.ModuleFactoriesResolver) typically during setting up the each test.
